          "max": 1.0,
          "def": 0.300000011920929,
          "unit": ""
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "EQ",
      "category": "Filter",
      "desc": "Single parametric peaking EQ band (RBJ biquad): Gain boosts or cuts a bell centred at Freq, with Q setting its width - narrow for surgical notches, wide for broad tone shaping. Chain several for a full parametric EQ. See GraphicEQ for fixed bands and the analog pack (Pultec/Neve/SSL) for coloured curves.",
      "ins": [
        "Audio"
      ],
      "numIns": 1,
      "params": [
